ALTER TABLE t1 PARTITION BY range columns(Z0_TEST0) SUBPARTITION BY range columns(Z0_TEST0) (PARTITION P1 VALUES LESS THAN('M') (SUBPARTITION part01 VALUES LESS THAN('A'), SUBPARTITION part02 VALUES LESS THAN('B'), SUBPARTITION part03 VALUES LESS THAN('C'), SUBPARTITION part04 VALUES LESS THAN('D'), SUBPARTITION part05 VALUES LESS THAN
